{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1659ebbb35","title":"中共中央关于处理南京东善桥林场林木被盗伐事件给南京市委的指示","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"4979d18cc7","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":12,"articleId":"1659ebbb35"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"12db4d3cf8","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于处理南京东善桥林场林木被盗伐事件给南京市委的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1659ebbb35"},{"id":"8f6ac4c535","type":"appellation","text":"南京市委，并告华东局及刘邓：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1659ebbb35"},{"id":"d22556b560","type":"paragraph","text":"南京新华社十一月四日发来南京东善桥林场遭破坏新闻一件，内称：在五月底至七月底两月间，由于军管会经济部农林组军事代表蒲吉五的官僚主义不负责任，该林场被乡民大规模盗伐松木七万二千六百余株，合干材四万三千担以上，被破坏面积一千四百余亩。请示可否发表。我们认为，此事如属实，应予发表，并必须彻查责任，予当事人以处分并向全国公布。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1659ebbb35"},{"id":"69dffa4c3a","type":"paragraph","text":"望将情况与执行情形电告。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1659ebbb35"},{"id":"f08faffc00","type":"subtitle","text":"中  央","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1659ebbb35"},{"id":"8d46cf28cd","type":"paragraph","text":" 十一月十二日","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1659ebbb35"}],"page":{"id":"ca868f019d","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"1659ebbb35","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}